elements.name: User Login in the Adactin Application.

steps.name: User launch the Adactin web application.
User enter the user name in the username field.
User enter the password in the password field.
User after given the login details click the login button to navigate to search hotel page.

elements.name: User search hotel page in Adactin Application.

steps.name: User have to select mandatory for preffered location in search hotel page.
User have to select preffered hotels in search hotel page.
User have to select preffered Room Type in search hotel page.
User have to select mandatory for the number of rooms in search hotel page.
User have to select mandatory for adults per room in search hotel page.
User have to select children per room in search hotel page.
After selcted all the fields and click search button to navigate select hotel page.

elements.name: User Select hotel page in Adactin Application.

steps.name: User have to select mandatory the hotel from the select hotel page.
User have to click continue button to navigate Book a hotel page.

elements.name: User book a hotel in Adactin Application.

steps.name: User mandatory to enter the First name in First name field.
User mandatory to enter the Last name in Last name field.
User mandatory to enter the Billing Address in Billing Address field.
User mandatory to enter the Credit Card No in Credit Card No field.
User mandatory to select the preffered credit card type to select in credit card type.
User mandatory to select the Expiry month to select in credit card type.
User mandatory to select the Expiry year to select in credit card type.
User mandatory to enter the CVV number to enter in the CVV number.
User have to click Search button to navigate Booking Confirmation page.

elements.name: User booking confirmation page in Adactin Application.
